Comment: The species was reported from Iran by Hölzel (1972) based on a single female specimen, but later it was characterized as a boreal species leading to its exclusion from the Iranian antlion fauna (
Mirmoayedi et al. 2015
). Our study suggests that the distribution of this species in Iran is restricted to the Caspian Coast province of Mazandaran .

